    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_shipping_costs",
      "label": "Show shipping costs section",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "shipping_costs_title",
      "label": "Section title",
      "default": "Shipping Costs"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "shipping_costs_content",
      "label": "Content",
      "default": "<p>Shipping charges for your order will be calculated and displayed at checkout.</p><p><strong>Free Shipping:</strong> We offer free standard shipping on all orders over $50 within the continental United States.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "International shipping"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_international",
      "label": "Show international shipping section",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "international_title",
      "label": "Section title",
      "default": "International Shipping"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "international_content",
      "label": "Content",
      "default": "<p>We currently ship to select international destinations. International shipping times vary by location and typically range from 7-21 business days.</p><p><strong>Customs and Import Duties:</strong> International customers are responsible for any customs fees, import duties, or taxes imposed by their country. These charges are not included in our shipping costs.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Order tracking"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_tracking",
      "label": "Show tracking section",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "tracking_title",
      "label": "Section title",
      "default": "Order Tracking"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "tracking_content",
      "label": "Content",
      "default": "<p>Once your order has shipped, you will receive an email confirmation with a tracking number. You can track your package using this number on the carrier's website.</p><p>Please allow 24-48 hours for tracking information to become available.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Shipping issues"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_issues",
      "label": "Show shipping issues section",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "issues_title",
      "label": "Section title",
      "default": "Lost or Damaged Packages"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "issues_content",
      "label": "Content",
      "default": "<p>If your package is lost in transit or arrives damaged, please contact us immediately. We will work with the shipping carrier to resolve the issue and ensure you receive your order.</p><p>For damaged items, please provide photos of the packaging and product to help us process your claim quickly.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Contact information"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_contact",
      "label": "Show contact section",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "contact_title",
      "label": "Section title",
      "default": "Questions About Shipping?"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "contact_content",
      "label": "Content",
      "default": "<p>If you have any questions about our shipping policy or your specific order, please don't hesitate to contact our customer service team.</p><p>Email: support@yourstore.com<br>Phone: 1-800-123-4567<br>Hours: Monday - Friday, 9am - 5pm EST</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Highlight box"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
